				noBgColor
				mbg-blue" style="background-color:;"> 
              <img loading="lazy" src="/content/dam/digicert/images/homepage/entrust-webinar-homepage-hero.png" alt="Entrust Webinar Homepage Hero Image" style="position:absolute;
					 top:-20px; right:0px;
