             <div class="descriptionBox whiteBox right top20" style="background-color: ;"> 
              <div class="description"> 
               <h6>REPORT</h6> 
               <h3>2024 State of Digital Trust</h3> 
               <p>Industry experts agree: digital trust is critical to protecting everything we connect. Read the 2024 report to learn more.<br> </p> 
               <div class="btn-container vertical"> <a href="/campaigns/digital-trust-survey" class="btn primary blue" target="_self" style="margin-right:px;
				 			    margin-bottom:px;"> Read the report</a> 
               </div> 
