           <div class="graphic-text-carousel-content"> 
            <div class="grid-12 vspacebtncomp
			ht-top20
			design1"> 
             <div class="blue-box left top20
			   " style="background-color: #0174c3;"> 
              <div class="blue-box--design1"></div> 
             </div> 
             <div class="imgBox left
				"> 
              <div style="margin-top: 0px;
			 		 margin-right:0px;
			 		 margin-bottom:0px;
			 		 margin-left:0px;"> 
               <img loading="lazy" src="/content/dam/digicert/images/homepage/idc-whitepaper-homepage-carousel.jpg" alt="IDC Whitepaper Homepage Carousel Image"> 
              </div> 
             </div> 
             <div class="descriptionBox whiteBox right top20" style="background-color: ;"> 
              <div class="description"> 
               <h6>WHITEPAPER</h6> 
               <h3>The Digital Trust Imperative</h3> 
               <p>Digital trust is a measure of confidence and assurance for everything that connects around the world. Read the IDC study.<br> </p> 
